              "name": "style",
              "summary": "A custom style specification to be applied to this component's Element.  Should be a valid argument to\r\n{@link Ext.Element#applyStyles}.\r\n<pre><code>\r\nnew Ext.Panel({\r\n    title: 'Some Title',\r\n    renderTo: Ext.getBody(),\r\n    width: 400, height: 300,\r\n    layout: 'form',\r\n    items: [{\r\n        xtype: 'textarea',\r\n        style: {\r\n            width: '95%',\r\n            marginBottom: '10px'\r\n        }\r\n    },\r\n        new Ext.Button({\r\n            text: 'Send',\r\n            minWidth: '100',\r\n            style: {\r\n                marginBottom: '10px'\r\n            }\r\n        })\r\n    ]\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\n"
